\begin_layout Section
Introduction
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This is the user manual for the program 
\family typewriter
FMC
\family default
 (from Focal Mechanisms Classification).
 This program has been developed on Python 2.7.3 and adapts some of the 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
key "gasp03"

\end_inset

 FORTRAN routines to obtain the different parameters of the earthquake focal
 mechanisms depending on the input format.
 Several output formats are eligible and a classification diagram for the
 focal mechanisms is produced.
 The input and output formats are the same used by the GMT program 
\family typewriter
psmeca
\family default
 in order to make the program integration easiest and facilitate the mapping
 of the data.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The program basically takes the focal mechanisms data, computes the different
 parameters that can be obtained, classifies each focal mechanism in one
 of seven possible types, and optionally outputs the parameters in different
 formats and generates a classification diagram from the input data.
\end_layout

